parameters:
The shallow valley, perfect for a summer retreat, in this
pollution-free island has clear water.

I didn't know there was a place like this... I'll tell
everyone about it later in the evening.

I finished the irrelevant incident with Saruyama, and
with a feeling that there might be something... I
decided to look around the waterfall.
It's not like I'm suddenly interested in Kanae's panties.

And it's not like I'm trying to find the money to buy
panties for me.

I'm not a man who worries about such trivial things, nor
am I a man with poor financial circumstances.

I just want to catch Saru or any monkey that caused the
incident.

However, not only have I never seen a monkey on this island,
but even if I were to actually encounter one, I can't
guarantee that I would be able to catch it.

...Even if I were to retrieve the panties now, they would
surely be torn to shreds...

As I pondered about various things and looked around near
the waterfall, a sparkling light that was different
from the reflection of water entered the corner of my
field of vision.
No, to be precise, they punched me in the eye.

If I were to keep my eyes wide open in vain searching for
monkeys, I feel like I would be blinded by the intense
reflection of light.

I tightly squeezed my eyes shut with both hands, and
slowly, gently opened them.
There, a silver, slender iron bar was placed all by itself.

This metal rod doesn't match the natural look of this
waterfall at all.
Yes, it's just like an antenna...
I don't think I could see it when I came here earlier...
I decided to bring the antenna back to the cottage.
I threw Akane, who was by the water into the river.
I mean I threw her in a technical sense.

Due to my lack of strength, Akane barely made a
curve being thrown at this height.

Akane, it's such a pity that you don't know the
greatness of playing in the river...!
But why would you throw me in the river...?!
Oh, Akane, your butt has turned bright red.

This is sexual harassment, right? There's no doubt that
this is sexual harassment, right?!
Akane, who is far away, sprays water towards me.

Akane sighed as she watched me sitting leisurely at the base
of a tree, and she lay down on the water's edge with
her arms and legs spread out.

The sight of only breasts and a face floating on the
water's surface was quite a pleasant view.

Actually, I couldn't even imagine that I would become this close
with Akane when we first met.

That's because Akane was the most famous person among famous
people at our university.

I think there are more people who know Akane than people
who know the name of the student council president.
What's wrong all of a sudden? You're spacing out...

No, I was just thinking about when I first met Akane.
Maybe she mistook me for a fan.

Ah, now that you mention it, I wonder if that's how it
was.

Nooo! At that time, there were really a lot of those kind of
things happening!
Yeah yeah, let's just leave it at that.
It's not about that! Ah, jeez.
Well, for me, it was a grateful story.

In the end, because I was mistaken for a fan, that's why
I was able to talk to Akane like that.

Thanks to that, there were many events where I could talk to
Akane on the way to the gym and participate in
tournaments to support her.

That was also one of the few enjoyable things in my college
life, I thought.
Anyway, there were few active events in my department.
The valley is nice, isn't it?
The valley is nice, isn't it?
